column5: Congratulations!!

Thanks everyone. He was born on the 18th and we are already back home from the hospital. My 2 year old ran over to see him for the first time and kissed him. They are now laying together on the floor. A moment to remember for sure!
Congratulations on a beautiful little boy. In no time he will be fishing along with his big brother and father. Cangratulations once again
Congrats. Can't wait for my second one. 6 months left.
THATABOY!!!!!!!!! now get a rod in his hands!!!!!!!
Good for you Bud... plenty of fun to come.... Averys graduating from Grade 8 tonite... another milestone in his life with many more to come... be proud papa!
Congrats to you and your significant other
WONDERFUL NEWS. Congrats to all.
that is soooo awesome!  Contrats!  Cheers!
Congrats!!
Congrats on the Little Guy,  BM
Congratulations Dan!
CONGRATS!!!!!
What did ya name him? (Or we gonna have a poll first? Lol)
lol We named him Jamie Daniel Bouck  My wife wanted Malcolm as a middle name but I figured I'd call him Malcolm in the Middle all the time!
Sweet!!
Awesome Bud!!  Keep em coming!!
AWESOME!!! He's a cutie!!! Start him young, a rod in his hands from the time he's 6 months old and he'll kick KVD's butt on the Pro Bass circuit!!!
Concrats Dan always a great feeling to bring home a new born.   good thing you kept the Suburban to haul around all that baby stuff.
Congratulations Dan!!
One more Angler born! Congrats!
My 2nd son just came tonight. 7 pounds 12 ounces and perfectly healthy
ahhh.. congrats!!!
congrats
Congrats to you and your wife  Rob
Congrats on the new fishin' partner.....
Congrats to both of you, Dan. It's gotta be the best miracle going.
ATTA BOY!    A chip off the old block! Give him a hug for me,Dan.
Congrats Dan, hope the baby and momma are doing well.  Has he got a fishing pole yet??
Congrats. Wishing you all the best.  Just JOHN
Congrats!!!
Great news Dan!! Congratulations!   Your life just got twice as good!
Congratulations!
That's great news Dan, congrat's to you and your wife!
Great stuff, that's one more rod (or two) in the boat!
Congrats!
Nice job!  they are cool dudes when they are little aren't they?
Congrats on the little man!
Congratulations Pop.  JF
Congrats Dan! Wish you and your wife a hopefully soon restful night!
thats great news, congratulations on the new arrival.  jason
Well done and congrats on another limit in the boat! HH
Congrats on the keeper!
congrats "daddy"! how come u look so pooped.. didn't SHE do all the work? lol  splashhopper and botbot
Congratulations...was he born on the 18th, or the 19th.  My son turned two yesterday!
Wonderful News, Congrats to you and the Miss's!
